Achievements.Name: Space Combat Award
Achievements.Description: Awarded for participating in fighter combat in outer space.

Achievements.Name: Schlos Base Defense Award
Achievements.Description: Awarded for stopping enemy attacks on Schlos Base.

Achievements.Name: Aegis of the People Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for escorting the 7 refugee ships to safety.

Achievements.Name: TCAF Luna Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for bravery beyond the call of duty to escort allied vessels to safety.

Achievements.Name: TCAF Mars Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for bravery beyond the call of duty under fierce enemy attacks.

Achievements.Name: Soldier's Charm Amulet
Achievements.Description: Given to you by Raymond as a token of his trust.

Achievements.Name: White Griffons Patch
Achievements.Description: Awarded to the commander and pilots of the White Griffon Squadron when it is formed.

Achievements.Name: TCAF Jupiter Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for bravery beyond the call of duty during withdrawal of the allied fleet.

Achievements.Name: Furious Pursuit Badge
Achievements.Description: Awarded for diligently shooting down large numbers of enemy ships.

Achievements.Name: Solo Aerospace Combat Award
Achievements.Description: Awarded for descending into the atmosphere and engaging in combat alone.

Achievements.Name: Operation Nebula Blaze Award
Achievements.Description: Awarded for fulfilling duty and fighting bravely in this difficult operation.

Achievements.Name: Guilty Roses Patch
Achievements.Description: Awarded for repelling the enemy Guilty Roses Squadron.

Achievements.Name: Super Battleship Slayer Patch
Achievements.Description: Awarded for shooting down the second S battleship supporting the enemy fleet.

Achievements.Name: TCAF Terra Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for shielding the fleet to allow its safe escape.

Achievements.Name: Hellfires Patch
Achievements.Description: Awarded for repelling the enemy Hellfire Squadron.

Achievements.Name: Night Ravens Patch
Achievements.Description: Awarded for challenging and eradicating the enemy Night Raven Squadron.

Achievements.Name: Solar System Defense Award
Achievements.Description: Awarded for great achievement during the campaign to defend the Solar System.

Achievements.Name: Special Operations Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for heroism in destroying the enemy's main weapon.

Achievements.Name: 1,000 Units Destroyed Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for shooting down 1,000 enemy fighters and attackers in space combat.

Achievements.Name: 10,000 Units Destroyed Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for shooting down 10,000 enemy fighters and attackers in space combat.

Achievements.Name: Ship Hunter Award
Achievements.Description: Awarded for shooting down 100 warships in space combat.

Achievements.Name: Gigaton Club Patch
Achievements.Description: Awarded for downing several enemy vessels with a combined weight of one gigaton.

Achievements.Name: Weapon Lord Patch
Achievements.Description: Awarded for collecting all usable equipment for the Delta Saber.

Achievements.Name: TCAF Pilot's Commendation
Achievements.Description: Awarded to the greatest pilots in the TCAF.
